Units 


px - fixed 
%  - Depending on parent 
vm - viewport width  (Depending on Screen width)
vh - viewport height (Depending on Screen height)

vmax -viewport maximum (width or height)
vmin -viewport minmum (width or height)


em - changed according to parent fontsize value when child use em 

1rem = 16 pixel it changed according to root 

ch - used charcter like if 20ch then only 20 characters in lines  

lh - height according to line 
